@node "limitations" "Limitations"

  Limitations of unregistered version

  Unregisterd versions are limited in their use as they  lack  certain
  functions.   Nevertheless   they   give   you  excellent  source  of
  information to check out what you should  register  for.  Also  very
  boring and time absorbing requesters appear very often. Complete and
  fast registered  version  is  available  upon  @{"registration." link registration 0}  Please
  support good and cheap software.

@endnode
