@node "smartiemenu" "Smartie menu"

  Smartie window's menu

  Smartie window is preferences window it enables to specify many
  parameters for processing of packed files or executables.

  @{" Project " link smartieproject 0}@{" Settings " link smartiesettings 0}@{" Startup " link smartiestartup 0}

@endnode
@node "xpkmenu" "XPK menu"

  XPK window's menu

  XPK window serves as packing/unpacking interface for XPK standard.
  You can drop files on it, load files with requester, compress or
  decompress them with lots of parameters.

  @{" Project " link xpkproject 0}@{" Misc " link xpkmisc 0}@{" Settings " link xpksettings 0}

@endnode
